
Begin by running the client and server 


This server to client communication allows the client to:

"ls" - list files in server directory

"lls" - List files in local directory 

"get" - gets a file from the server Usage: get <file-name>

"put" - sends a file to the server directory Usage: put <file-name>

"size" - Gets the size of a file in the server Usage: size <file-name>

"lsize" - Gets the size of a file in the client Usage: lsize <file-name>

"mget" - Gets a list of files similar to the "get" method 
Usage: mget <file-name> <file-name2> <file-name3> .......